works.description: For those who crave for excellence, exclusivity and choice, the makers of horological machines, Maximilian Büsser & Friends (MB&F) has now added the new Horological Machine N°3 Frog to its “Frog” family. Christened HM3 Frog Zr (aka Black Frog), the stunning timepiece brings a sense of playfulness into high-end watchmaking. The “Zr” adds to the name owing to the fact that this is the first offering from the house that is done in zirconium. Zirconium is a metal similar to titanium but even tougher.
